**NLHS Minimum Acceptable Standards:**
- ITIL4: Level 3 (Defined) minimum
- NIST CSF: Tier 2 (Risk Informed) minimum, prefer Tier 3
- Support: 24/7 for critical clinical systems
- Change Management: Adequate or better

